values:
Oh, I received yesterday a scottish terrier puppy >_<*
I called her Aiko (against my mother will ^O^*, who hates japanse names).
Oh, I missed so much a dog during the last year...my previous dog, Rara, died on june 2003, and I really couldn't accept the idea of having a new dog.
Plus, my mother absolutely wanted to buy another West Higland White Terrier, despite the fact that nobody in my family wanted a clone of the poor Rara.
But, finally, yesterday afternoon, she's arrived. Aiko chan!!!!! >_<*
I couldn't choose the right name....Momo or Aiko, Momo or Aiko....but she absolutely have an Aiko face!!!
^O^* Now she's sleeping on her little sofa >_<*
Kawaiiiiiiiii!!!!!!
